{
  "texts": [
    "Finally, Table 9 shows the test results of seven classic caption generation models and the DIC-Transformer model.",
    "In this paper, there are seven comparison methods used for image caption generation tasks, which are roughly divided into two categories: one is the top-down method, and the other is a bottomup approach.",
    "Experiments show no significant difference between top-down and bottom-up approaches.",
    "For example, the ShowTell method exhibits the worst results in the top-down method, whereas the Fc method performs the best effect, showing little difference from the optimal method in the bottom-up method.",
    "The model with the highest CiderD score is AoANet, with a value of 431.09."
  ]
}